text: Diplomatic missions in Eswatini This is a list of diplomatic missions in Eswatini (formerly known as Swaziland). At present, the capital city of Mbabane hosts seven embassies/high commissions. The Eswati government does not publish a diplomatic list online, so the information on this page has been gathered from various other sources, including foreign ministries online.
